name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.ha.fencing.ssh.connect-timeout
description:
SSH connection timeout, in milliseconds, to use with the builtin
    sshfence fencer.

name: tfile.fs.input.buffer.size
description: Buffer size used for FSDataInputStream in bytes.

name: fs.s3a.retry.limit
description:
Number of times to retry any repeatable S3 client request on failure,
    excluding throttling requests.

name: mapreduce.reduce.shuffle.fetch.retry.interval-ms
description:
Time of interval that fetcher retry to fetch again when some
  non-fatal failure happens because of some events like NM restart.
